</use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530294\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530294\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 25, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nkl1665702536608.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nkl1665702536608.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nkl1665702536608.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nkl1665702536608\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets the specified widget property to a given value.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__topic_d128216e1_d128217e1_d128218e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__p_d128219e1_d128220e1_d128221e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Object</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">setProperty</span>(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__section_w1887ab1b5b3_w1888ab1b5_w1889ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d252558e83\">Arguments </h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__parml_jdn_ty3_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">PropertyName</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the widget property.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__section_w1890ab1b5b5_w1891ab1b5_w1892ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d252558e101\">Return Value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__parml_uw5_vy3_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">New value for the specified widget property.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__section_w1893ab1b5b7_w1894ab1b5_w1895ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d252558e119\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__section_w1896ab1b5b9_w1897ab1b5_w1898ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d252558e136\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__p_d128243e1_d128244e1_d128245e1\">The initial values of the widget properties of a\n        component, entity, occurrence, or field can be set declaratively in the Properties\n        Inspector, and procedurally in ProcScript using the following commands:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__ul_g5l_yy3_dwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">For components: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$componentproperties</span> and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instanceproperties</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__li_d46397e1_d46398e1_d46399e1\">For entities: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entityproperties</span>\n          and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curentproperties</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__li_d46400e1_d46401e1_d46402e1\">For occurrences: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occproperties</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__li_d46403e1_d46404e1_d46405e1\">For fields: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__p_d128246e1_d128247e1_d128248e1\">Once the DSP is loaded, the values of these properties\n        can be dynamically changed in the browser using the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setProperty</span> and\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setProperties</span> API functions.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__p_d128249e1_d128250e1_d128251e1\">You can use the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">clearProperties</span>\n        function to reset all the widget properties of the object to their initial values.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__section_el2_r2x_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d252558e197\">Example: Using setProperty</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__p_d128255e1_d128256e1_d128257e1\">In the following example,\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setProperty</span> is used to set the HTML property display to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">none</code>, thereby hiding the field.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104nkl1665702536608_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"nkl1665702536608__codeblock_c1v_zy3_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">webtrigger detail ; for field HIDE\n scope\n endscope\n javascript\n this.getParent().getField(\"MYFIELD\").setProperty(\"style:display\", \"none\");\n endjavascript\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sno1665702583691.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pym1665702536682.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>clearProperty()</a><p>Restores the initial value of the specified property.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwh1665702536527.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getProperty()</a><p>Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbz1665702536840.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setProperties()</a><p>Sets widget properties for a Uniface data object in JavaScript.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Entity</a><p>The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mvn1752068459777.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$componentproperties</a><p>Return or set the definition-time widget properties of the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afr1752069080308.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instanceproperties</a><p>Return or set the current runtime widget properties of current instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530294\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530294\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "setProperty() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 25, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sets the specified widget property to a given value. Return = Object . setProperty ( PropertyName , Value ) Arguments PropertyName Name of the widget property. Return Value Return New value for the specified widget property. Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Description The initial values of the widget properties of a component, entity, occurrence, or field can be set declaratively in the Properties Inspector, and procedurally in ProcScript using the following commands: For components: $componentproperties and $instanceproperties For entities: $entityproperties and $curentproperties For occurrences: $occproperties For fields: $properties and $fieldproperties Once the DSP is loaded, the values of these properties can be dynamically changed in the browser using the setProperty and setProperties API functions. You can use the clearProperties function to reset all the widget properties of the object to their initial values. Example: Using setProperty In the following example, setProperty is used to set the HTML property display to none , thereby hiding the field. Explain this code webtrigger detail ; for field HIDE scope endscope javascript this.getParent().getField(\"MYFIELD\").setProperty(\"style:display\", \"none\"); endjavascript end Copy Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser. clearProperty() Restores the initial value of the specified property. getProperty() Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object. setProperties() Sets widget properties for a Uniface data object in JavaScript. $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. uniface.Entity The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. $componentproperties Return or set the definition-time widget properties of the current component instance. $instanceproperties Return or set the current runtime widget properties of current instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}